  "description": "A working procedure for identifying genring in a specific media artifact: identify the depicted people, inventory what is selected and excluded, identify the codification, trace the substitution work, locate the structural function, and identify the genre-coherence pressure. Requires background knowledge of the depicted people's actual living variety.",
  "name": "How to Identify Genring in a Media Artifact",
